// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0373 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 22614586-f08e-5949-abf2-b215b5a29d2c

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
